reviewText:
First this was not a dvd a expected but a poor to view VCR with distorsion all over it .The movie was supposed to be Misty losing her virginity and they couldn't found a worse candidate to do it .Some little greasy wimp who was smaller than Misty and walked around spouting off his nonesense blathering with his brooklyn accent the whole time. Worse was he had the nerve to have sex and run,leaving misty shocked and in tears .The jerk was allowed to come back for a  secong chance but I am sure most of the Misty fans were not happy seeing our girl treated like a common whore. We all like her because she is a beauty of the highest order.

The whole thing lacked realism and even the sex scene with Juian Wells at the end coulnd't save this production. However if sex with a male was this bad ,no wonder Misty chose to go lesbian.
